{"tid":2355932,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日晚餐 壯陽大補餐","createTime":"2021-01-06T12:27:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T06:26:46.000Z","uid":260581,"like":30,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d7face1389db8225e31aa1427bb0e905493883da","tid":2355932,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:27:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QbnEF2G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQbnEF2G.jpg&h=5752afda&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/snWaNHH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsnWaNHH.jpg&h=f15d4187&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b5S1UnJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb5S1UnJ.jpg&h=f39b745f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今朝買唔到吞拿魚<br />\n所以轉左買蠔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n藍盤係bays of fire<br />\n原本我淨係買半打，但後面個女人話金盤既st helens 好好食，所以我買多半打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBays of fire好creamy, st helens雖然冇咁creamy, 但成個感覺比覺中和同清香，仲有淡淡海水味，真係冇介紹錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之兩打都好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外我拎左4隻加蒜蓉辣椒焗，正正常常<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af6183ba1b19a60fa00c17637e242d8c3051167","tid":2355932,"uid":2920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:28:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c21510ec6a6b5de98cfcaf49bdfe1e79ca317040","tid":2355932,"uid":272819,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:28:21.000Z","msg":"城晚美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但香港不美了"},{"pid":"849d24fcedba